  <prompt>Implement Phase 1D transitive memberships per spec.md FR-1D.1, FR-1D.2, FR-1D.3. Promoted to firm in-scope by owner 2026-06-20. 1-hop max enforced (Q3).</prompt>
  <goal>Endpoint accepts `?includeRelated=documents,events`. Returns transitive memberships (e.g., documents on matters I'm on). Response shape extends byRole with nested keys.</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec FR-1D.2">Max chain depth = 1 hop (Q3); deeper requests rejected with 400</constraint>
    <constraint source="NFR-04">p95 ≤300ms target maintained or documented limit</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md §A">BFF pre-merge checklist</constraint>
  </constraints>
  <knowledge>
    <topic>transitive-membership-chained-discovery</topic>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/patterns/dataverse/web-api-client.md</file>
      <file>.claude/patterns/dataverse/relationship-navigation.md</file>
      <file>projects/spaarke-platform-foundations-r3/spec.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>
  <steps>
    <step order="0">Context check + FR-1D.1, FR-1D.2, FR-1D.3, Q3</step>
    <step order="1">Extend MembershipResolverService.ResolveAsync to accept includeRelated[]</step>
    <step order="2">For each related entity, discover its Lookup fields back to the primary entity</step>
    <step order="3">Build chained FetchXML: primary IDs → related IDs</step>
    <step order="4">Extend MembershipResponse.byRole with nested structure (e.g., byRole.documents.{role})</step>
    <step order="5">Update endpoint to parse includeRelated query param</step>
    <step order="6">Reject deeper chains with 400 BadRequest</step>
    <step order="7">Integration tests</step>
  </steps>
  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">includeRelated=documents returns matter→document transitive memberships (AC-1D.1)</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Multi-hop request returns 400 BadRequest</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">p95 within budget OR limit documented (AC-1D.2)</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
